description: Department of Elections - Elected Mr. Aliyar Umarkatha Jabeer as Chairman of the Irakkamam P/S - Elected Mr. Welliwela Gedara Chaminda Sanath as Chairman of the Naula P/S - Elected Mr. Beruwala Arachchige Ruwan Smarawickrama as a Member of the Naula P/S - Elected Mr. Carder Meera Sahiubu Mohamed Rafeek as a Member of the Biyagama P/S.
